{"tid":2018950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國就台灣參與世衛大會向世衛發外交照會","createTime":"2020-05-16T02:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T03:17:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4bcb1514e744a12a92812a73cb733fb25f1839","tid":2018950,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"德國就台灣參與世衛大會向世衛發外交照會<br />\n16.05.2020 09:38<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生大會將於下星期一舉行，台灣傳媒報道，德國外交部發言人證實上星期已經聯同其他國家，向世衛秘書處提出外交照會，並與英國、法國和美國等國家，聯名致函給世衛總幹事譚德塞，促請對方邀請台灣，以觀察員身分參加世衛大會。發言人又指，德國認為以觀察員身分參加世衛大會，毋須以國家為前提，相信台灣的參與有助於對抗新型冠狀病毒疫情。<br />\n<br />\n台灣一直爭取參加世衛大會，但北京表明反對。世衛早前表示，收到13個國家提案，邀請台灣參加今年的世衛大會，但由於成員國意見分歧，總幹事譚德塞未獲授權發出邀請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287858&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287858%26csid%3D261_341&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b2e6496d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287858&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4de5f91cb785a4b9c3070b2478589fb91e59f853","tid":2018950,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Task1 Task2 Task3  Like retweet reply</span><br />\nTwitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=5ad1da9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=d959bc4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https